        "Objective\n",
        "\n",
        "The primary objective of this project is to develop a Recurrent Neural Network (RNN) model for automatic news text classification using the AG News dataset from Hugging Face. The project preprocesses raw news articles through text cleaning, tokenization, sequence padding, and label encoding before training the model. An Embedding layer is used to convert words into dense vector representations, a Simple RNN layer learns sequential patterns and contextual information from the text, and a Dense layer with Softmax activation predicts the appropriate news category. Finally, the trained model is evaluated on unseen test data and used to classify new news articles into one of the predefined categories."
      ],
